@node KeyMail

    @{fg shine}@{b}MultiRen is Key-mail Ware@{ub}
    ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~@{fg text}

  MultiRen is now Key-mail Ware which means that you have
  to send @{"me" link Author} an e-mail with your name (or another acceptable string
  to be in the registration field) to get a key-file so you can
  get rid of all annoying requesters and stuff! :-)

  Then you will also be able to use the "Skip annoying requesters.."
  feature!

    @{fg fill}Please use the @{b}Easy registering..@{ub} in the menu,
    or when you start the program!    @{i}Thanks. @{ui}@{fg text}

  It's absolutely free, I just want to get a clue about how many
  users actually found this program :)

  Your name will of cource not be used for anything else
  than to create your personal keyfile which will be sent
  back to you ASAP.

  When you receive your keyfile, put it in S:, ENVARC: or
  the same directory as MultiRen itself.


@endnode

